title: Queen - Knebworth Park 86 (live bootleg - actually Mannheim) FLA
description:
Info taken from http://www.queenonstage.com/mywebpage/knebworth.htm
-------------------------------------------------------------------

KNEBWORTH PARK '86 

1 CD

Label: Devil Records  008  

Country: Brazil 

Released: 1998 (Info on cover)  

Recorded: Meimaktgelande Mannheim, Germany   June 21st. 1986 

Sound: Excellent stereo soundboard recording. Radio FM broadcast. 

Comments: Rare Brazilian bootleg cd. Fake info on cover being 'Knebworth Park' 1986. 
 Recording are from Mannheim, Germany '86. Just a part of the show.
 Only for interest for 'mania' collectors. I have listen true the hole cd, and it IS the Mannheim concert whatever anyone else say's. 
Roots: Originally from a radio broadcast. Heavily bootlegged on vinyl & CD's. Too much titles to mention.    

Time:  72:48
